    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，结构搭好了。我先在main上提交a，然后分出三个分支。branch1上提交j，main继续提交b，branch2提交x，branch3提交u。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit id:a",
        "commit id:j",
        "commit id:b",
        "commit id:x",
        "commit id:u"
