    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来让main再提交c，然后branch3先合并main。之后main提交d，最后branch1和branch2依次合并main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit id:c",
        "commit id:d",
